    AvailableOrders

    The availableOrdersPageController class controls the functionality of the available orders page.

    CanceledReport represents a report containing information about canceled automatic, manual, and not-come orders, along with their corresponding percentages.

    The canceledReportGraphController class controls the functionality of the canceled report graph page.
